        <body><div type="writingSession" n="1"><p>Herzliche Grüße!</p><closer>Ihr <signed>Arthur</signed></closer><postscript><p>Morgen ab nach <rs ref="#pmb3704" type="place">Algier</rs></p></postscript></div><div type="writingSession" n="2"><p><handShift scribe="#pmb2173"/>Haben in <rs ref="#pmb263" type="place">Florenz</rs> in einem Variete besonders heftig Ihrer gedacht – was Sie nun neugierig machen möge!</p><closer>Herzlichst <signed>Olga.</signed></closer></div></body>
